            <h2>Pretrial Audit System</h2>
            <h4>Nov. 2024 - Present</h4>
            <p><strong>Association:</strong> Harris County</p>
            <p>
              <strong>Technologies Used:</strong> C#, .NET, Razor Pages, SQL
              Server
            </p>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Lead Developer</p>
            <p>
              Designed and developed from the ground up, this C# .NET-based
              software solution leverages Razor Pages and SQL Server to
              streamline the case audit process. The system enforces user
              authentication and access control, enhancing security alongside
              efficiency, accuracy, and consistency. It automates routine tasks,
              provides intuitive auditor interfaces, and generates insightful
              reports to improve audit quality and decision-making.
            </p>
           
