          <div class="project-card">
            <h2>Justice Center Navigator</h2>
            <h4>Jan. 2023 - May 2023</h4>
            <p>
              <strong>Association:</strong> Harris County, University of
              Houston-Clear Lake: Capstone Project
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Technologies Used:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript,
              Node.js, MongoDB, Raspberry Pi
            </p>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Lead Developer</p>
            <p>
              Designed to assist defendants and visitors at the Criminal Justice
              Center in Downtown Houston, this self-service kiosk enhances
              navigation and access to court information.<br /><br />
              The system runs on a Raspberry Pi 4 with a 7” touchscreen and is
              housed in a custom 49” wooden pedestal for visibility and ease of
              use. The Pi launches a web application in kiosk mode, displaying
              building directories, Misdemeanor/Felony court schedules, and
              real-time defendant docket information from a cloud database.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/hbrandon15/criminal-justice-kiosk"
