              Senior Project
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Technologies Used:</strong> Python, ROS, OpenCV, Google
              Voice API, Linux
            </p>
            <p><strong>Role:</strong> Project Manager</p>
            <p>
              Developed a voice-controlled drone that integrates face tracking
              to enhance standard drone capabilities. The system enables voice
              commands for launching and landing while using the onboard camera
              to detect and track human faces. As Project Manager, I ensured
              deadlines and requirements were met, facilitated team
              communication, resolved conflicts, and contributed to Python
              module development.
            </p>
